snippets.title: BareMetalSolution listInstances Sample
snippets.description: List servers in a given project and location.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution getInstance Sample
snippets.description: Get details about a single server.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution updateInstance Sample
snippets.description: Update details of a single server.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution renameInstance Sample
snippets.description: RenameInstance sets a new name for an instance. Use with caution, previous names become immediately invalidated.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution resetInstance Sample
snippets.description: Perform an ungraceful, hard reset on a server. Equivalent to shutting the power off and then turning it back on.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution startInstance Sample
snippets.description: Starts a server that was shutdown.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution stopInstance Sample
snippets.description: Stop a running server.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution enableInteractiveSerialConsole Sample
snippets.description: Enable the interactive serial console feature on an instance.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution disableInteractiveSerialConsole Sample
snippets.description: Disable the interactive serial console feature on an instance.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution detachLun Sample
snippets.description: Detach LUN from Instance.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution listSSHKeys Sample
snippets.description: Lists the public SSH keys registered for the specified project. These SSH keys are used only for the interactive serial console feature.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution createSSHKey Sample
snippets.description: Register a public SSH key in the specified project for use with the interactive serial console feature.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution deleteSSHKey Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a public SSH key registered in the specified project.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution listVolumes Sample
snippets.description: List storage volumes in a given project and location.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution getVolume Sample
snippets.description: Get details of a single storage volume.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution updateVolume Sample
snippets.description: Update details of a single storage volume.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution renameVolume Sample
snippets.description: RenameVolume sets a new name for a volume. Use with caution, previous names become immediately invalidated.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution evictVolume Sample
snippets.description: Skips volume's cooloff and deletes it now. Volume must be in cooloff state.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution resizeVolume Sample
snippets.description: Emergency Volume resize.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution listNetworks Sample
snippets.description: List network in a given project and location.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution listNetworkUsage Sample
snippets.description: List all Networks (and used IPs for each Network) in the vendor account associated with the specified project.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution getNetwork Sample
snippets.description: Get details of a single network.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution updateNetwork Sample
snippets.description: Update details of a single network.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution createVolumeSnapshot Sample
snippets.description: Takes a snapshot of a boot volume. Returns INVALID_ARGUMENT if called for a non-boot volume.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution restoreVolumeSnapshot Sample
snippets.description: Uses the specified snapshot to restore its parent volume. Returns INVALID_ARGUMENT if called for a non-boot volume.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution deleteVolumeSnapshot Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a volume snapshot. Returns INVALID_ARGUMENT if called for a non-boot volume.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution getVolumeSnapshot Sample
snippets.description: Returns the specified snapshot resource. Returns INVALID_ARGUMENT if called for a non-boot volume.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution listVolumeSnapshots Sample
snippets.description: Retrieves the list of snapshots for the specified volume. Returns a response with an empty list of snapshots if called for a non-boot volume.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution getLun Sample
snippets.description: Get details of a single storage logical unit number(LUN).

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution listLuns Sample
snippets.description: List storage volume luns for given storage volume.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution evictLun Sample
snippets.description: Skips lun's cooloff and deletes it now. Lun must be in cooloff state.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution getNfsShare Sample
snippets.description: Get details of a single NFS share.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution listNfsShares Sample
snippets.description: List NFS shares.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution updateNfsShare Sample
snippets.description: Update details of a single NFS share.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution createNfsShare Sample
snippets.description: Create an NFS share.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution renameNfsShare Sample
snippets.description: RenameNfsShare sets a new name for an nfsshare. Use with caution, previous names become immediately invalidated.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution deleteNfsShare Sample
snippets.description: Delete an NFS share. The underlying volume is automatically deleted.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution listProvisioningQuotas Sample
snippets.description: List the budget details to provision resources on a given project.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution submitProvisioningConfig Sample
snippets.description: Submit a provisiong configuration for a given project.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution getProvisioningConfig Sample
snippets.description: Get ProvisioningConfig by name.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution createProvisioningConfig Sample
snippets.description: Create new ProvisioningConfig.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution updateProvisioningConfig Sample
snippets.description: Update existing ProvisioningConfig.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution renameNetwork Sample
snippets.description: RenameNetwork sets a new name for a network. Use with caution, previous names become immediately invalidated.

snippets.title: BareMetalSolution listOSImages Sample
snippets.description: Retrieves the list of OS images which are currently approved.
